  "title": "Performance Sales & Marketing",
  "description": "<p>📈 <strong>Performance Sales & Marketing Executive (Entry Level – Face-to-Face Sales)</strong><br /><strong>On-Ground Marketing | Full Training Provided | Fast Career Progression</strong></p><p>This is a <strong>frontline, people-facing sales and marketing role</strong>, not a digital marketing or desk-based position.</p><p>As a Performance Marketing Executive, you’ll be trained to represent brands through <strong>direct, face-to-face customer engagement</strong>, execute sales-driven marketing campaigns, and track real performance results. High performers progress quickly into <strong>team leadership and campaign management roles</strong>.</p><p>If you enjoy interacting with people, working on the ground, and being rewarded for results, this role is for you.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Execute <strong>face-to-face sales and marketing campaigns</strong></p></li><li><p>Engage customers directly to promote and represent client brands</p></li><li><p>Drive conversions and track daily performance results</p></li><li><p>Learn campaign planning, execution, and optimisation</p></li><li><p>Develop leadership skills and progress into managing teams and campaigns</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Provide</strong></h3><p>📚 Structured training from day one (no experience needed)<br />📈 Clear, performance-based career progression<br />💰 <strong>Uncapped commission</strong><br />🌱 Development in communication, confidence, and leadership<br />🔥 Young, driven, and supportive team environment</p><h3><strong>Who This Role Is For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates / ORD personnel / career switchers</p></li><li><p>Individuals who enjoy <strong>face-to-face interaction and sales execution</strong></p></li><li><p>Motivated by performance, growth, and advancement</p></li><li><p>Strong learning attitude with leadership potential</p></li></ul><p>⚠️ <strong>Important:</strong><br />This role involves <strong>direct sales and on-ground marketing execution</strong>.<br />It is <strong>not</strong> a digital marketing, content, or office-only role.</p><p>👉 <strong>Apply now</strong> if you’re looking for a hands-on sales role with real growth opportunities.</p>",
